::Kluster::

Kluster looks from Phobia to Hysteria. "Those crates contain the technology 
needed to build spare engines. If you could check it for compatibility with 
out systems and for any bugs, it'll be really great of ya," he says, turning 
to Phobia and turning serious.

He shakes his head. "Scans have showed that the Iron Fist is at least as 
strong as this ship. Probably stronger. Even with superior manueverability, 
the Cybertronian Fire will be too damaged to make the trip back to Cybertron, 
which is the reason we were sent here in the first place."
